    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A variety of emerald green (a toxic copper-based pigment), perhaps invented by Baron von Mitis in Vienna.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
